byline.original: By RICK GLADSTONE and THOMAS ERDBRINK

lead_paragraph: President Hassan Rouhani, speaking at the United Nations, warned that American credibility would suffer if the United States undercut the accord with “illegal actions.”

headline.main: Iran’s President Accuses U.S. of ‘Lack of Compliance’ on Nuclear Deal
headline.print_headline: U.S. Flouting Nuclear Deal, the President of Iran Says
